title: CDDIS_VLBI_products_eop
summary: Earth Orientation Parameters (EOPs) product derived from analysis of Very Long Baseline Interferometry (VLBI) data. These products are the generated by analysis centers in support of the International VLBI Service for Geodesy and Astrometry (IVS).
